title: Try
lyrics:
We can stumble in and out of love
I can never seem to call it fun
But I'll try, try, try
I'll try, try, try
I'll try to make it alright



We played lovers in the fallin' rain

You can't tell me that it's just a game



So you'll try, try, try

You'll try, try, try



Oh, I found a new way

To die

It's hidden in your tear stained eyes



Oh, I never wanna hear you say

Say it like I did that day

What love's over now

That love is over now



So I'll try, try, try

I'll try, try, try



Oh, I found a new way

To die

It's hidden in your eyes

Oh, I- I found a new way

To die

It's hidden in your tear stained eyes
